By":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢個社會 有樓就解決左9成問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係十成 因為個個都既得利益者 冇人搞反共 港獨之類</blockquote><br />\n個個有樓，d樓就唔值錢了</blockquote><br />\n值唔值錢關我撚事<br />\n我想住得舒服小小渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係<br />\n住屋係基本<br />\n呢家d撚屌儲十幾年買到300尺<br />\n就當自己人生贏家</blockquote><br />\n所以話到依家個社會都唔撚暴動真係好撚奇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39161d150d4f6b19515d550ee47a775f89238ee","tid":142721,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:09:07.000Z","msg":"上一代一樣大把人買唔到樓住公屋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多人打工人工低餐搵餐食餐餐清"},{"pid":"f19635bc1185b496727b5399e4daec001180fd4e","tid":142721,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:11:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上一代一樣大把人買唔到樓住公屋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多人打工人工低餐搵餐食餐餐清</blockquote><br />\n香港有70%人有儲蓄習"},{"pid":"c430497d60b75a982a3927bb3ffeb2b49de2465b","tid":142721,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如個個訓街  到時唔到政府唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好on9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n垃圾正苦口話壓抑樓價<br />\n其實d政策推高樓價"},{"pid":"778ce15e206c48dc3759d9e99206cd274960bdb7","tid":142721,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:16:15.000Z","msg":"用11月辣招做分水嶺<br />\n<br />\n整體物業成交的確少左 但只係少20%<br />\n但二手樓登記數字足足少左40%+<br />\n<br />\n而家政府明益地產商 推晒d人炒一手樓 發展商唔怕開天殺價<br />\n而二手樓業主亦跟住一手樓叫價 偶有天價成交<br />\n造成破新高新聞 <br />\n而家業主企硬呢個&quot;benchmark&quot;唔放 享受呢個帳面上升"},{"pid":"1858744bcbe93b52e5c6f098cce7274fb7bed9b1","tid":142721,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:17:05.000Z","msg":"根本除左無樓人仕<br />\n樓價升，個個受益<br />\n<br />\n狗官<br />\n有樓人仕<br />\n稅收<br />\n地產商<br />\n進貢強國<br />\n消化產能過盛<br />\n地產代理<br />\n起樓既一堆人仕<br />\n炒樓人仕<br />\n<br />\n咁多利益和咁多利益人仕<br />\n梗係繼續gogogo，將來3萬一呎，10萬一呎"},{"pid":"2e43519ad44d167ab3a3ee074b57ba3eddbdab9e","tid":142721,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:17:42.000Z","msg":"On9先信正苦想壓抑樓價<br />\n<br />\n正苦既角度梗係愈高愈好"},{"pid":"6ef94cfce0663439cd351188e9e254ba034f7bf5","tid":142721,"uid":86097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:26:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d7460da27ae251eb7edd8e19cf1d9007ce04d53","tid":142721,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:27:35.000Z","msg":"好正常<br />\n<br />\n之前蘋果訪問個男人<br />\n2005 年用$108 萬買咗層五百幾呎樓<br />\n做九成幾按，月供幾千蚊<br />\n依家$108 萬夠比首期咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b1020a009c02ae3181c1ad266b5150160e9fec","tid":142721,"uid":47575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:29:48.000Z","msg":"屌都on99<br />\n<br />\n除去真係好撚叻 好撚多窿路 好有人賞識既小量個別人仕<br />\n正正常常一個普通打工仔<br />\n一個月都可能只係儲到幾千至三萬<br />\n<br />\n當你儲到三萬一個月<br />\n一年先三十六萬<br />\n十年先三百六十萬<br />\n邊個撚屌敢寫包單十年後樓價依舊?<br />\n<br />\n望返十年前既人工同物價<br />\n再望下依家既人工同物價<br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n<br />\non99"},{"pid":"789862ebcd2b617de7f89bc8f9d9d0c4065463bc","tid":142721,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:38:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上一代一樣大把人買唔到樓住公屋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多人打工人工低餐搵餐食餐餐清</blockquote><br />\n香港有70%人有儲蓄習</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" c